Located in the highly coveted Telge Ranch community. Featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, 1 half bath, covered patio, and a spacious 2-car garage, every detail has been carefully designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Don't miss this opportunity to turn this house into your dream home.
